{"_id":"5HnOtuIPqSo9GuWE","name":"Exploit Weakness","content":"<p>These weapons are small and able to slip into gaps in a target’s defenses. Attacks with this weapon treat full armor as partial armor, and partial armor as unarmored (but do not actually reduce the location’s AR). This can be used to trigger effects, such as Slashing, that interact with the level of armor the target is wearing.</p>","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"eeXhsDlbzUBZOXZT":3},"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_qtm3mdw5kon","path":"References#/CF_SEP/Qualities#/CF_SEP/Weapon Qualities","color":"#000000"}}}
{"name":"Deafened","content":"<p>The character loses the ability to hear. deafened characters cannot hear anything and automatically fail tests that rely on hearing.</p>","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"eeXhsDlbzUBZOXZT":3},"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_hw0xe1g9xxt","path":"References#/CF_SEP/Conditions","color":"#000000"}},"_id":"5lClajCL1KJWDoRT"}
