{"name":"Reinforced Knuckles","content":"<p>Can only be applied to Arm location armour. Adds +1 ENC. This location counts as being a Cestus. The smith must choose which weapon material to make the cestus from as when creating any other weapon. This weapon is part of the armour and cannot be disarmed. It has the durability of the armour rather than the weapon.</p>","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"eeXhsDlbzUBZOXZT":3},"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_u0ce34u73r","path":"References#/CF_SEP/Qualities#/CF_SEP/Armour Qualities","color":"#000000"}},"_id":"DDVnkISlWim8N8HE"}
{"_id":"DfC1501wL64oIckY","name":"Entangling","content":"<p>Attacks with this weapon cannot be parried or blocked. Instead of dealing damage, a successful attack with this weapon forces the opponent to make a Strength or Agility test. If they fail, they suffer a -20 penalty to all combat tests as they become entangled. They can use an action to repeat the test and free themselves on success.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>If this effect was applied by a melee attack, then if the target character leaves the melee ranged of the Entangling weapon then the character wielding the weapon must choose to either let go of their weapon (maintaining the effect on the target), or keep their weapon (removing the effect from the target). </p>","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"eeXhsDlbzUBZOXZT":3},"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_qtm3mdw5kon","path":"References#/CF_SEP/Qualities#/CF_SEP/Weapon Qualities","color":"#000000"}}}
{"name":"Fur Lined","content":"<p>+10 pr X to resist effects of cold.</p>","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"eeXhsDlbzUBZOXZT":3},"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_u0ce34u73r","path":"References#/CF_SEP/Qualities#/CF_SEP/Armour Qualities","color":"#000000"}},"_id":"DviZyH463RxlxEfi"}
{"name":"Mindlock","content":"<p>The caster's maximal capacity for Mindlock is equal to their maximal Action Points, representing the ability to divide attention between the mental battle to control the ctreautre, and paying attention to one's surroundings. When a summoned creature is destroyed, banished, or released, the Mindlock is reduced, freeing up capacity for new minions.</p>\n<p>If the conjurer's maximal Action Points are reduced while in control of a Daedra, they must immediately roll an opposed willpower test against the conjured Daedra. The Daedra gain a bonus +1 DoS per Mindlock the conjurer is unable to provide to the reduced capacity. </p>\n<p>If the Daedra wins the opposed test, it becomes unbound exactly as described in the Summon [Daedra/Construct] trait.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>Creatures bound by Necroamncers rarely serve of their own free will and only has 1 AP per round to obey their master's order. A secondary action can be used by the necromancer in order to remove the minion's 1 AP limit.</p>","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"eeXhsDlbzUBZOXZT":3},"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_ysrtxwqxmu","path":"References#/CF_SEP/Qualities#/CF_SEP/Spell Attributes","color":"#000000"}},"_id":"DyA3yhRJDDDu8cTw"}
{"name":"Overload","content":"<p>The caster benefits from an extra effect (as specified) if not restraining this spell.</p>","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"eeXhsDlbzUBZOXZT":3},"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_ysrtxwqxmu","path":"References#/CF_SEP/Qualities#/CF_SEP/Spell Attributes","color":"#000000"}},"_id":"ELRN5yhwQUASYJXL"}
{"name":"Free Actions","content":"<p>Free Actions can be taken at any time during the combat round, and cost no action points to activate, though the GM should keep in mind what is reasonable for a character to achieve in six seconds.</p>","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"eeXhsDlbzUBZOXZT":3},"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_oklt7qkfm8k","path":"References#/CF_SEP/Combat#/CF_SEP/Actions","color":"#000000"}},"_id":"H1FN8P9TR5rkpP1n"}
{"_id":"H74ao7uTiZrIVyUW","name":"Focus","content":"<p>Character treats the hand holding the weapon as a free hand for the purposes of casting spells. The weapon does not increase the range of any spell, due to it’s reach.</p>","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"eeXhsDlbzUBZOXZT":3},"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_qtm3mdw5kon","path":"References#/CF_SEP/Qualities#/CF_SEP/Weapon Qualities","color":"#000000"}}}
{"_id":"HZisCgJniNzIO8vD","name":"Spiked Head","content":"<p><span style=\"color:#191813\">Increases Crushing value by 2*X on All Out Attack, decreases Crushing by 2*X on normal attacks. </span></p>","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"eeXhsDlbzUBZOXZT":3},"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_qtm3mdw5kon","path":"References#/CF_SEP/Qualities#/CF_SEP/Weapon Qualities","color":"#000000"}}}
