{"name":"Invisible","content":"<p>Invisible characters cannot be seen. Characters fail all sight related tests related to spotting the character, and attack them at a -30 penalty, assuming they can guess where they might be in the first place.</p>","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"eeXhsDlbzUBZOXZT":3},"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_hw0xe1g9xxt","path":"References#/CF_SEP/Conditions","color":"#000000"}},"_id":"ShazAWRXSiPT6Gwf"}
